{{For|other universities that use the '''UMT''' mnemonic|UMT (disambiguation){{!}}UMT}} {{Infobox university |name=Metropolitan University of Tirana |native_name=Universiteti Metropolitan i Tiranës |logo= |endowment= |image= Universiteti Metropolitan i Tiranës.svg |image_size= 200px |latin_name= |established= 2011 |type=Private university. Study levels offered: [[Bachelor's degree|Bachelor]], [[Master's degree|Master]] |staff= |rector=Prof. Dr. Agim Selenica |faculty= |students= |city=[[Tirana]] |country=[[Albania]] |campus= |affiliations=[[University Iuav of Venice]], [[Frederick University]], [[University of Prizren]], London Trade Association<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.umt.edu.al/PunoMeNe/Partnere.aspx |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-12-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111031002930/http://www.umt.edu.al/PunoMeNe/Partnere.aspx |archivedate=2011-10-31 |df= }}</ref> |colors = |website=[http://www.umt.edu.al www.umt.edu.al] }}
The '''Metropolitan University of Tirana''' ({{lang-sq|Universiteti Metropolitan i Tiranës}}), abbreviated '''UMT''', is a [[private university]] located in [[Tirana]], [[Albania]]. It was founded in 2011, by a group of architects and engineers as the only [[List of universities in Albania|Albanian university]] on [[information technology]], engineering and architecture.
