'''École [[Marie Félicité Brosset]]''' is a French-Georgian international school in [[Tbilisi]], [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]],now making part of "Rober Schuman European School" . It has a double studying program - in French and Georgian and gives its students possibility to continue their education in France,after passing the baccalauréat exam. 
The average quantity of students is about 80-100.

